lead_paragraph: Workers began removing the large letters spelling out the Trump name from the shuttered Trump Plaza casino in Atlantic City on Monday after real-estate mogul Donald Trump sued to end a licensing deal that allowed the casino owners to use his name.

headline.main: Workers Begin Removing Trump Name From Atlantic City Casino
